WEBVTT

00:24.640 --> 00:25.710
Yingge Courtyard?

00:28.230 --> 00:30.690
I used to dream about leaving here
every day.

00:30.800 --> 00:33.840
I never thought
I would come back to reminisce one day.

00:35.600 --> 00:36.280
Follow me.

00:47.470 --> 00:48.870
What are you looking for?

01:06.680 --> 01:07.540
My grandmother

01:08.680 --> 01:10.680
left this jade pendant to my mother.

01:11.350 --> 01:14.480
And she passed it on to me
before she passed away.

01:15.230 --> 01:16.510
Back when we were in Yingge Courtyard,

01:16.510 --> 01:18.310
I already wanted to give it to you.

01:18.310 --> 01:20.440
But I didn't know your feelings for me,

01:21.280 --> 01:22.590
so I never did.

01:25.120 --> 01:27.310
When we left the courtyard in a rush.

01:28.039 --> 01:30.770
So I couldn't take this jade pendant
away with me.

01:33.680 --> 01:35.680
Now that we've returned here again,

01:36.680 --> 01:38.509
maybe it's fate.

01:46.590 --> 01:47.200
Chu,

01:48.350 --> 01:50.479
can we forget everything from the past

01:50.940 --> 01:52.200
and be together again?

02:16.190 --> 02:18.910
I expected that you wouldn't accept
this jade pendant.

02:18.910 --> 02:20.440
I've made too many mistakes

02:20.560 --> 02:21.760
and already lost you.

02:23.800 --> 02:25.660
I just held on to a glimmer of hope,

02:26.520 --> 02:28.120
wanting to try one last time.

02:30.590 --> 02:31.240
Yan Xun.

03:59.540 --> 04:04.950
[REBIRTH]

04:05.370 --> 04:07.980
[Episode 36]

05:19.160 --> 05:20.490
Through the woods ahead

05:20.560 --> 05:22.480
is the southernmost part of Great Yan.

05:22.480 --> 05:24.480
To the west are Ximeng and Biantang.

05:24.870 --> 05:26.270
To the east is Great Yong.

05:26.600 --> 05:29.310
We can either go through Great Yong
to the southern border,

05:29.310 --> 05:31.680
or settle in a nearby village.

05:32.920 --> 05:34.390
This place is close to the Pale Tribe

05:34.390 --> 05:36.320
with convenient transportation.

05:36.430 --> 05:38.310
If we get tired of living here one day,

05:38.310 --> 05:40.110
we can change places at any time.

05:43.040 --> 05:44.440
Do you remember Yunzhou?

05:47.680 --> 05:49.610
You mean Yunzhou next to Biantang?

05:49.680 --> 05:50.190
Yes,

05:50.920 --> 05:52.180
it's not far from here.

05:53.440 --> 05:56.120
When we returned to Great Yan
from Biantang,

05:56.150 --> 05:57.550
we passed through there.

05:58.390 --> 06:00.120
I heard from the merchants there

06:00.120 --> 06:01.680
that it's situated at the junction

06:01.680 --> 06:04.040
of Great Yong, Great Yan, and Biantang.

06:04.510 --> 06:05.840
It's an ungoverned area

06:06.160 --> 06:07.680
but also a thriving commercial hub.

06:07.680 --> 06:11.040
We can sell silk from Biantang
to Great Yong,

06:11.560 --> 06:14.800
or horses and jade from Great Yan

06:15.310 --> 06:16.230
to Biantang.

06:17.560 --> 06:18.720
No matter what we do,

06:19.360 --> 06:20.890
we can live a peaceful life.

06:21.120 --> 06:21.680
Okay.

06:22.830 --> 06:23.890
I'll listen to you.

06:24.830 --> 06:25.750
Let's go there.

06:30.070 --> 06:31.000
Have you heard?

06:31.720 --> 06:33.380
The world is going into chaos.

06:33.720 --> 06:35.050
Our envoy from Biantang

06:35.870 --> 06:37.270
was killed in Great Yong.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.000
Not to mention

06:39.120 --> 06:40.510
our envoy,

06:40.720 --> 06:42.720
I heard that even Yan Xun,
King of Great Yan,

06:42.720 --> 06:44.650
and Chu Qiao are trapped in Great Yong.

06:44.650 --> 06:46.000
No one knows if they are dead or alive.

06:46.000 --> 06:47.270
Don't talk nonsense, you two.

06:47.270 --> 06:49.430
Our king is safe and sound
in the Capital of Great Yan.

06:49.430 --> 06:50.750
Didn't he kill the rebels

06:50.750 --> 06:52.880
from Lanchuan and Helian not long ago?

06:53.070 --> 06:54.130
It's not nonsense.

06:54.630 --> 06:56.620
Doing business here every day,
how would you know?

06:56.620 --> 06:58.390
We just came out
of the Capital of Great Yan.

06:58.390 --> 07:01.040
Those days, troops and horses
were coming and going on the streets,

07:01.040 --> 07:03.160
with only a female general in command.

07:03.160 --> 07:05.600
We didn't see your King of Great Yan
show up at all.

07:05.600 --> 07:06.800
If he's not trapped in Great Yong,

07:06.800 --> 07:07.730
then where is he?

07:08.360 --> 07:09.000
Exactly.

07:09.160 --> 07:10.070
You still can't talk nonsense.

07:10.070 --> 07:11.240
-Cheng Yuan.
-Stop drinking the tea.

07:11.240 --> 07:11.680
Go.

07:11.680 --> 07:12.750
Whatever, I don't care.

07:12.750 --> 07:13.510
Go.

07:13.950 --> 07:15.510
No one would like
to come to this shabby place.

07:15.510 --> 07:16.600
Go.

07:44.720 --> 07:46.510
I bought this in a nearby town.

07:46.950 --> 07:49.680
It will take you several days
to reach Great Yong.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.460
It'll be a tiring journey.

07:52.070 --> 07:54.600
I've prepared
some extra dry rations for you.

07:58.130 --> 07:58.659
Helian.

07:58.690 --> 07:59.330
I know.

08:03.920 --> 08:05.000
In your heart,

08:05.720 --> 08:07.050
Yan Xun matters so much.

08:07.430 --> 08:08.760
If you don't go save him,

08:09.720 --> 08:11.520
we won't be able to live in peace.

08:12.560 --> 08:14.510
Besides, he is the King of Great Yan.

08:14.510 --> 08:16.040
If anything happens to him,

08:16.720 --> 08:18.560
Great Yan will definitely fall into chaos.

08:18.560 --> 08:19.680
Our Helian Tribe

08:19.680 --> 08:21.880
is also one of the 13 tribes of Great Yan.

08:22.160 --> 08:23.600
When the nest is overturned,

08:23.600 --> 08:24.860
no egg remains intact.

08:25.360 --> 08:27.120
We both understand this truth.

08:31.800 --> 08:32.909
But promise me

08:33.360 --> 08:34.960
that no matter what happens,

08:36.480 --> 08:38.000
you must come back safely.

08:39.510 --> 08:41.309
I will always be waiting for you.

08:47.000 --> 08:47.720
Helian,

08:48.510 --> 08:49.390
I promise you.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.440
Once I find Yan Xun,

08:53.390 --> 08:54.840
I will return safely.

09:04.870 --> 09:06.070
We will go to Yunzhou,

09:07.630 --> 09:09.510
or anywhere you want to go,

09:10.440 --> 09:12.500
and live a life with just the two of us.

10:01.270 --> 10:02.330
What is this place?

10:02.600 --> 10:04.320
What's hidden under the white clothes?

10:04.320 --> 10:07.380
I heard it's the newly built
Temple of the Faceless God.

10:16.840 --> 10:19.770
Kneel down quickly.
This is the Imperial Preceptor.

10:32.270 --> 10:33.510
With blood as the pact

10:34.030 --> 10:35.290
and fire as the medium,

10:35.550 --> 10:36.790
Faceless God,

10:36.870 --> 10:38.150
please hear my call.

10:38.510 --> 10:41.170
Punish the evil
and destroy the disrespectful!

10:43.320 --> 10:43.980
Last night,

10:44.360 --> 10:46.420
the Faceless God descended before me

10:47.320 --> 10:49.600
and bestowed 3 sacred prophecies.

10:50.390 --> 10:52.790
When the 3 prophecies
are fulfilled one by one,

10:52.790 --> 10:54.480
she will personally descend to the world

10:54.480 --> 10:56.750
and save all people from torment!

10:57.000 --> 10:57.600
What does that mean?

10:57.600 --> 10:59.320
The first prophecy of the Faceless God

10:59.320 --> 11:02.270
is to punish 4 deeply sinful people,

11:02.910 --> 11:06.840
using their blood
to cleanse the filth of the.

11:06.840 --> 11:08.550
Punish the sinful people?

11:08.790 --> 11:09.960
What does that mean?

11:09.960 --> 11:11.960
Does it mean someone is going to die?

11:19.960 --> 11:21.670
I heard something happened
to the Master of the Muhe family.

11:21.670 --> 11:24.530
Their young master is rushing back
for the funeral.

11:31.270 --> 11:33.200
Isn't that General Meng's cousin?

11:33.390 --> 11:35.720
Did anything happen to General Meng, too?

11:41.030 --> 11:42.360
Among the 4 great clans,

11:42.720 --> 11:43.920
2 have had accidents.

11:44.670 --> 11:47.030
And also General Meng,
Commander of the Southwest Forces.

11:47.030 --> 11:49.240
Now, the military power in the southwest

11:49.240 --> 11:50.200
has all been handed over

11:50.200 --> 11:52.260
to the Zhuge family and the Mu family.

11:53.270 --> 11:54.600
Among the 4 great clans,

11:55.080 --> 11:57.610
only the Mu family
is Zhao Che's trusted ally.

11:57.960 --> 12:01.080
The Muhe family and the Wei family
both belong to Zhao Yang's faction.

12:01.080 --> 12:03.810
General Meng works
for the Emperor of Great Yong.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.600
Zhao Che wants to use
the Faceless God Sect

12:05.600 --> 12:07.200
to get rid of his dissidents.

12:07.240 --> 12:08.030
In this case,

12:09.630 --> 12:13.290
the Emperor of Great Yong will soon become
Zhao Che's puppet, too.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.770
There's one more thing.

12:14.790 --> 12:15.390
What is it?

12:15.960 --> 12:17.760
In the Faceless God's prophecy,

12:18.200 --> 12:19.800
4 people are supposed to die.

12:20.390 --> 12:21.200
Now,

12:22.270 --> 12:23.600
there is still one left.

12:25.390 --> 12:26.240
It's Xing Le.

12:27.790 --> 12:30.440
Half of Great Yong's outer armies
are in his hands.

12:30.440 --> 12:32.390
If Zhao Che wants to control Great Yong,

12:32.390 --> 12:34.120
he will definitely target him.

12:34.960 --> 12:36.200
We have to save Xing Le.

12:36.200 --> 12:36.750
Chu,

12:38.270 --> 12:40.270
you know I have a deep blood feud
with Great Yong.

12:40.270 --> 12:41.730
If they start infighting,

12:42.030 --> 12:44.160
I'd like to watch them kill each other.

12:44.510 --> 12:47.770
Are you sure you want to meddle
in this unnecessary matter?

12:49.120 --> 12:49.750
Yan Xun.

12:51.360 --> 12:53.390
This is absolutely not
an unnecessary matter.

12:53.390 --> 12:55.600
I agreed to leave Great Yong
with you back then

12:55.600 --> 12:56.750
because you told me

12:57.000 --> 12:57.800
that Great Yan

12:57.960 --> 12:59.820
was an independent and just land,

13:01.270 --> 13:03.440
but it was destroyed
by the Emperor of Great Yong.

13:03.440 --> 13:04.150
Now,

13:05.000 --> 13:06.360
Zhuge Yue and I have gone through

13:06.360 --> 13:08.270
all the hardships to build such a place,

13:08.270 --> 13:10.150
yet it is still not welcomed
by the world.

13:10.150 --> 13:12.510
There is no such thing
as a peaceful sanctuary.

13:12.510 --> 13:14.960
If the deep-rooted problems
of Great Yong are not resolved,

13:14.960 --> 13:15.720
this world

13:16.670 --> 13:18.730
will never take a turn for the better.

13:19.440 --> 13:20.390
Leave this to me.

13:20.720 --> 13:21.650
Wait for my news.

13:23.840 --> 13:25.360
Congratulations, Prince of Jing.

13:25.360 --> 13:27.480
Among the 4 great clans in Zhenhuangcheng,

13:27.480 --> 13:29.630
the Muhe family
and the Wei family have both fallen.

13:29.630 --> 13:32.390
General Meng, who held the southwest
military power, also died suddenly.

13:32.390 --> 13:34.510
From now on,
among the 4 great clans of Great Yong,

13:34.510 --> 13:37.040
only yours remains dominant,
Prince of Jing.

13:37.240 --> 13:41.000
That is all thanks to the Crown Prince.

13:41.360 --> 13:42.440
But I'm wondering

13:43.550 --> 13:45.410
about what His Highness promised

13:46.120 --> 13:48.450
regarding the southwest military power.

13:55.150 --> 13:58.630
The spies of Qingshan Manor
will act tonight.

13:58.790 --> 14:00.390
Once General Xing Le is dead,

14:00.910 --> 14:02.440
the southwest military power

14:02.440 --> 14:04.770
will be handed over to you,
Prince of Jing.

14:07.390 --> 14:09.750
Thank you so much, Young Master Zhuge.

14:16.410 --> 14:18.530
[Qingzhu Hall]

14:33.080 --> 14:33.940
Show yourself.

14:35.120 --> 14:36.030
I know it's you.

14:40.960 --> 14:42.960
You are wanted throughout the city.

14:43.120 --> 14:44.720
Following me so recklessly,

14:45.030 --> 14:48.090
aren't you afraid
I'll order another crackdown on you?

14:49.320 --> 14:50.030
I know,

14:50.390 --> 14:52.120
with Wei Guang and Muhe Lie dead,

14:52.120 --> 14:54.920
the Wei and Muhe families' power
will surely wane.

14:55.360 --> 14:57.200
Of the 4 great families in Zhenhuangcheng,

14:57.200 --> 14:59.330
only the Zhuge and Mu families remain.

14:59.550 --> 15:00.270
Zhuge Yue,

15:00.550 --> 15:02.280
what exactly are you planning?

15:02.360 --> 15:04.290
We can work together to achieve it.

15:06.600 --> 15:07.530
What kind of plan

15:08.600 --> 15:10.000
do you think I could have?

15:10.120 --> 15:12.180
We've been through so much together.

15:12.550 --> 15:13.750
You can't deceive me.

15:14.000 --> 15:16.000
Back in the foul Zhuge's Residence,

15:16.000 --> 15:17.150
you pretended to be the aloof

15:17.150 --> 15:18.960
and ruthless Fourth Young Master
of Qingshan Manor.

15:18.960 --> 15:20.720
Yet, in this dog-eat-dog Zhenhuangcheng,

15:20.720 --> 15:21.670
you still saved me

15:21.670 --> 15:23.670
as well as the slaves like me.

15:23.670 --> 15:24.360
I believe

15:24.550 --> 15:26.600
you won't become a person who aids evil

15:26.600 --> 15:28.460
and cannot tell right from wrong.

15:29.750 --> 15:31.080
That conceited

15:31.670 --> 15:34.240
Fourth Young Master
who thought he could save the world

15:34.240 --> 15:35.240
is already dead.

15:36.360 --> 15:38.870
Now there is only the powerful official
of Great Yong,

15:38.870 --> 15:40.910
Chief of Qingshan Manor, Zhuge Yue.

15:47.550 --> 15:48.810
If you don't leave now,

15:49.270 --> 15:51.670
when the spies from Qingshan Manor arrive,

15:52.000 --> 15:53.530
you won't be able to escape.

15:57.270 --> 15:58.200
Zhuge Yue!

16:01.710 --> 16:02.440
Mr. Mu,

16:03.550 --> 16:06.150
sending so many Mu's Guards
to tail me late at night,

16:06.150 --> 16:07.240
what are you up to?

16:07.670 --> 16:09.510
Sorry, General Zhuge.

16:10.120 --> 16:13.500
[Mu Shen, from the Mu family's faction]

16:10.320 --> 16:11.480
I am just anxious

16:11.910 --> 16:15.510
to catch this female slave
to ease His Majesty's worries.

16:16.070 --> 16:18.240
I didn't expect you to be here, too.

16:19.390 --> 16:20.390
In this case,

16:21.320 --> 16:24.510
General Zhuge,
why don't you kindly step aside

16:25.200 --> 16:26.550
and let me kill her?

16:27.600 --> 16:31.670
So we can go ask for a reward
from the Crown Prince together.

16:33.550 --> 16:34.390
General Mu,

16:34.960 --> 16:36.670
this is all your credit.

16:37.120 --> 16:38.650
How could I get a share of it?

16:40.510 --> 16:42.080
General Mu, please go ahead

16:42.390 --> 16:45.200
and help the Crown Prince
solve the problems.

16:46.870 --> 16:49.670
Thank you for your understanding,
General Zhuge.

16:50.960 --> 16:51.630
Kill her.

17:01.840 --> 17:02.630
Huan Huan?

17:08.510 --> 17:09.770
Whoever kills Chu Qiao

17:09.790 --> 17:11.450
will receive a bounty reward!

17:14.349 --> 17:15.900
Since you are not afraid of death,
General Mu,

17:15.900 --> 17:17.099
I will grant you that!

17:19.349 --> 17:20.109
Let them go.

17:20.109 --> 17:21.310
Step back, everyone!

17:40.550 --> 17:41.960
Thank you for saving me today.

17:41.960 --> 17:42.920
Don't mention it.

17:42.920 --> 17:43.880
I owed you this.

17:45.590 --> 17:46.400
General Chu,

17:46.920 --> 17:48.920
I want to seek cooperation with you.

17:52.750 --> 17:53.750
We can cooperate.

17:54.400 --> 17:55.270
But I won't eat

17:55.270 --> 17:57.070
anything you give me ever again.

17:58.640 --> 18:01.550
Let me go! Let me go!

19:19.200 --> 19:20.000
General Xing.

19:20.400 --> 19:22.480
Thank you for saving me, General Chu.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.480
What did you find out from him?

19:25.480 --> 19:26.440
He insisted

19:26.830 --> 19:28.310
that he was not Zhao Che's accomplice

19:28.310 --> 19:30.510
and said he didn't know any of his plans.

19:31.750 --> 19:33.010
When pressed further,

19:33.110 --> 19:34.480
he started yelling

19:34.550 --> 19:35.550
and acting crazy.

19:41.030 --> 19:42.160
You knocked him out?

19:43.310 --> 19:44.790
He jumped around

19:44.790 --> 19:45.920
until he passed out.

19:52.070 --> 19:53.920
They have already come back and reported.

19:53.920 --> 19:55.640
General Xing Le was rescued,

19:55.640 --> 19:57.240
and his whereabouts remain unknown.

19:57.240 --> 19:57.960
Mu Shen was

19:59.160 --> 20:00.690
also taken away by Chu Qiao.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.880
They are no more than pawns.

20:04.750 --> 20:05.880
No need to feel pity.

20:07.310 --> 20:08.640
You promised me before

20:09.020 --> 20:11.720
that you wouldn't let Chu Qiao
interfere with our operation.

20:11.720 --> 20:12.720
But now.

20:13.400 --> 20:15.480
Without these pawns,

20:16.310 --> 20:18.310
this game of chess is at a stalemate.

20:21.550 --> 20:23.310
Qingshan Manor is already
searching the city

20:23.310 --> 20:25.350
for Chu Qiao and Yan Xun.

20:25.880 --> 20:28.400
Spies have been deployed
at all city gates.

20:28.550 --> 20:30.550
Even the slightest move they make

20:30.550 --> 20:32.880
won't escape the Qingshan Manor's watch.

20:35.920 --> 20:37.030
The second prophecy Jia Meng

20:37.030 --> 20:38.920
announced
in the Temple of the Faceless God

20:38.920 --> 20:40.030
says that the Faceless God

20:40.030 --> 20:41.720
would punish a land of sin

20:41.960 --> 20:43.820
and cleanse its sins with a flood.

20:44.480 --> 20:45.750
Since she said that,

20:45.750 --> 20:47.270
Ximeng has been experiencing
continuous heavy rain,

20:47.270 --> 20:49.070
and many mountains
have suffered from floods.

20:49.070 --> 20:51.470
The climate in Ximeng
is extreme by nature.

20:52.030 --> 20:53.550
The late summer and early autumn

20:53.550 --> 20:55.440
in previous years
also saw the heaviest rainfall.

20:55.440 --> 20:56.830
Continuous heavy rain at this time

20:56.830 --> 20:58.240
is nothing weird at all.

20:58.510 --> 20:59.310
But I am afraid

20:59.920 --> 21:02.250
only the local people of Ximeng know this.

21:02.640 --> 21:04.960
Others will believe
it is really the fulfillment

21:04.960 --> 21:06.290
of Jia Meng's prophecy.

21:06.750 --> 21:09.410
But what's in it for Zhao Che
with this prophecy?

21:10.160 --> 21:12.720
Is it just to make the Faceless God
more convincing?

21:12.720 --> 21:14.450
I am afraid it is more than that.

21:14.920 --> 21:16.580
Zhao Che's next step is likely

21:17.640 --> 21:19.300
to make a move against Ximeng.

21:20.510 --> 21:21.510
Your Highness,

21:22.510 --> 21:24.910
I know I once served
the Thirteenth Prince,

21:25.400 --> 21:26.880
and to earn your trust,

21:27.590 --> 21:29.070
I must first prove myself.

21:29.590 --> 21:30.510
And now,

21:31.160 --> 21:33.590
I have proven it to you with 2 prophecies.

21:34.720 --> 21:35.780
The first prophecy

21:36.440 --> 21:38.590
purged your dissidents in the court.

21:39.160 --> 21:40.760
Before the second prophecy,

21:41.240 --> 21:43.030
I observed the celestial phenomena.

21:43.030 --> 21:45.640
The heavy rain in Ximeng
will last for half a month,

21:45.640 --> 21:48.790
exactly fulfilling the cursed land.

21:52.400 --> 21:53.680
Well done.

21:54.270 --> 21:56.960
Tomorrow, the army of Great Yong
will depart from Zhenhuang

21:56.960 --> 21:57.920
to Ximeng.

21:58.350 --> 22:00.270
I will, in the name of the Faceless God,

22:00.270 --> 22:01.400
reclaim Ximeng.

22:01.920 --> 22:03.720
Once you get control

22:03.880 --> 22:05.680
of the black gold mine in Ximeng,

22:05.920 --> 22:07.380
not to mention Great Yong,

22:07.480 --> 22:11.110
all the realms will be in your hands,
Your Highness.

22:12.590 --> 22:14.030
General Meng is dead.

22:15.310 --> 22:17.310
The military power in the southwest

22:17.720 --> 22:20.580
shall be taken over
by the Prince of Jing from now on.

22:20.830 --> 22:22.240
For this march to Ximeng,

22:22.590 --> 22:24.750
we'll count on your strategic leadership.

22:24.750 --> 22:25.440
I

22:26.270 --> 22:27.330
accept your order.

22:28.550 --> 22:30.610
During the fierce battles back then,

22:31.110 --> 22:32.350
my leg

22:33.400 --> 22:36.720
was crippled while saving His Majesty.

22:37.160 --> 22:39.220
I didn't expect that because of this,

22:39.440 --> 22:41.550
I'd be discarded by His Majesty.

22:42.510 --> 22:45.880
All these years, I haven't been able
to share the burden of state affairs,

22:45.880 --> 22:47.110
idling away my time.

22:47.400 --> 22:48.110
Now,

22:49.160 --> 22:51.030
Your Highness, you entrust me
with such an important task,

22:51.030 --> 22:53.350
I'm deeply moved.

23:01.640 --> 23:03.240
Although I am old,

23:03.480 --> 23:04.720
my mansion

23:04.720 --> 23:07.590
is full of people willing to serve you,
Your Highness!

23:07.590 --> 23:09.160
Please rest assured, Your Highness.

23:09.160 --> 23:11.590
I will certainly not let you down.

23:27.400 --> 23:28.860
Judging by the direction,

23:29.510 --> 23:31.110
they must be leaving the city.

23:31.110 --> 23:32.350
You were right.

23:32.960 --> 23:35.590
Now, Zhao Che is using the heavy rainfall

23:35.750 --> 23:38.350
to claim to the world
that Ximeng enraged the Faceless God.

23:38.350 --> 23:39.590
By dispatching troops now,

23:39.590 --> 23:41.110
he is doing it
in the name of the Faceless God

23:41.110 --> 23:42.240
to take over Ximeng.

23:42.510 --> 23:43.970
Previously, Zhuge Muqing

23:44.160 --> 23:47.090
took 20,000 Yong Army soldiers
outside Ximeng Pass.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.680
They haven't retreated yet.

23:48.680 --> 23:51.550
Plus, the newly mobilized troops
from a few days ago.

23:51.550 --> 23:52.350
I'm worried

23:53.270 --> 23:54.680
He Xiao and the others
won't be able to hold out.

23:54.680 --> 23:55.640
Don't worry.

23:55.790 --> 23:57.680
I will set off right away
for Great Yan to mobilize troops

23:57.680 --> 23:58.750
to reinforce Ximeng.

23:58.750 --> 23:59.310
Okay.

24:06.350 --> 24:07.350
King of Great Yan,

24:07.640 --> 24:10.030
thank you for saving me that day.

24:11.110 --> 24:13.110
Zhenhuangcheng is now locked down.

24:13.110 --> 24:15.830
Take this token
and leave through the southeast gate.

24:15.830 --> 24:17.880
The defending general
at the southeast gate is my trusted aide.

24:17.880 --> 24:19.790
He will let you pass
when he sees the token.

24:19.790 --> 24:21.190
Thank you, General Xing.

24:21.400 --> 24:24.920
I will return to Great Yan to prepare
a counterattack as soon as possible.

24:24.920 --> 24:26.960
Zhao Che is completely
out of his mind now.

24:26.960 --> 24:29.310
Jia Meng has announced
2 prophecies so far.

24:29.310 --> 24:31.830
The next one will only be worse.

24:32.430 --> 24:33.760
You and Huan Huan must be

24:33.880 --> 24:35.410
very careful staying here.

24:36.350 --> 24:38.010
On behalf of the Faceless God,

24:38.110 --> 24:40.110
I'm announcing the third prophecy.

24:40.720 --> 24:42.240
On this land,

24:42.510 --> 24:45.000
the previous one chosen
by the Faceless God

24:45.160 --> 24:47.090
will be baptized by heavenly fire.

24:47.270 --> 24:49.030
From the ashes of the heavenly fire,

24:49.030 --> 24:51.400
the next one chosen by the Faceless God

24:51.400 --> 24:53.000
will descend upon the world!

25:01.870 --> 25:02.660
You may go.

25:07.110 --> 25:08.240
Where are you going?

25:10.400 --> 25:10.920
Go.

25:13.480 --> 25:14.140
You guys...

25:50.880 --> 25:51.590
Stop him.

26:24.030 --> 26:25.070
Zhuge Yue,

26:25.840 --> 26:27.080
you told me

26:27.100 --> 26:29.110
that as long as I took good care of Chu,

26:29.110 --> 26:30.270
you would come back.

26:31.270 --> 26:33.480
My Lord, the King of Great Yan is injured.

26:33.480 --> 26:35.880
Capture the King of Great Yan immediately.

27:23.840 --> 27:25.370
The Ice Arrow hurt the bone.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.200
Bear with it.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.240
Cheng Yuan,

27:53.310 --> 27:55.170
take the Black Eagle Army's token

27:55.790 --> 27:58.400
and rush back to Great Yan right away
to deploy troops and reinforce Ximeng.

27:58.400 --> 27:59.270
Zhao Che's troops

27:59.270 --> 28:01.200
are already on their way to Ximeng.

28:02.110 --> 28:02.790
Go quickly.

28:04.960 --> 28:05.680
Hurry!

28:10.270 --> 28:11.800
I will fetch you some water.

28:12.590 --> 28:13.350
Cheng Yuan.

28:45.640 --> 28:46.100
Come on.

28:57.550 --> 28:59.240
After Zhao Che conquers Ximeng,

28:59.240 --> 29:01.510
he'll target Great Yan next.

29:02.830 --> 29:05.790
You must fully support Chu in fighting

29:06.400 --> 29:09.310
against Great Yong,
just as you have assisted me.

29:09.880 --> 29:11.610
This is not just for Chu's sake,

29:11.640 --> 29:13.400
but also for the safety of Great Yan.

29:13.400 --> 29:14.930
I'll carry you back with me.

29:16.400 --> 29:17.000
No way.

29:17.550 --> 29:18.880
I have trouble moving now.

29:18.880 --> 29:20.510
It's too unsafe for you
to take me with you.

29:20.510 --> 29:22.160
People from Qingshan Manor are
all over outside.

29:22.160 --> 29:23.200
It's an emergency.

29:23.200 --> 29:23.930
You go first.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.240
I will be fine.

29:30.510 --> 29:32.350
I know you like Consort Helian.

29:35.550 --> 29:37.350
I will grant you marriage later,

29:40.160 --> 29:42.020
right at the foot of Mount Huihui.

29:42.200 --> 29:43.000
Your Majesty.

29:43.880 --> 29:44.680
Before,

29:46.230 --> 29:48.630
you didn't understand my feelings for Chu.

29:49.350 --> 29:50.160
Now,

29:52.480 --> 29:54.340
you should be able to understand.

29:59.480 --> 30:00.160
Cheng Yuan,

30:01.750 --> 30:03.210
you grew up without a home.

30:04.070 --> 30:05.400
You once told me

30:06.680 --> 30:09.410
that the military camp of Great Yan
was your home.

30:09.480 --> 30:10.590
Over the years,

30:11.240 --> 30:12.550
I have always hoped

30:12.890 --> 30:15.000
you could find someone you love

30:15.830 --> 30:17.590
and have a real home.

30:18.360 --> 30:21.080
Now I can finally...

30:25.030 --> 30:25.920
rest assured.

30:29.240 --> 30:30.040
Your Majesty.

30:43.890 --> 30:46.290
Young Master, there are bloodstains here.

30:49.070 --> 30:50.750
Search deeper into this forest.

30:50.750 --> 30:52.110
Make sure you bring the person back to me!

30:52.110 --> 30:52.750
Understood.

30:52.750 --> 30:53.280
Let's go.

30:57.400 --> 30:58.730
Cheng Yuan, go quickly!

30:59.480 --> 31:00.200
Leave now!

31:02.790 --> 31:05.250
Zhuge Yue and I have fought
for so many years.

31:05.270 --> 31:06.200
I can't kill him,

31:06.720 --> 31:08.180
and neither can he kill me.

31:08.240 --> 31:08.900
Cheng Yuan.

31:10.960 --> 31:12.820
I order you to leave immediately!

31:13.700 --> 31:14.240
Your Majesty...

31:14.240 --> 31:15.770
This is the King's command!

31:17.480 --> 31:18.540
Yes, Your Majesty.

31:26.950 --> 31:28.350
I'm sorry, Your Majesty.

31:29.310 --> 31:30.170
Over the years,

31:30.870 --> 31:32.720
we have been sovereign and subject

31:32.720 --> 31:33.850
as well as brothers.

31:34.070 --> 31:35.920
Forgive me, as your elder brother,

31:35.920 --> 31:38.180
for not listening to you again this time.

32:02.150 --> 32:02.910
It's Yan Xun!

32:06.580 --> 32:07.480
Catch him!

33:59.240 --> 34:00.270
Yan Xun.

34:29.880 --> 34:31.150
Zhuge Yue,

34:32.510 --> 34:35.030
you lost.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.360
We've fallen for a trick.

35:02.760 --> 35:04.760
The King of Great Yan must be nearby.

35:05.480 --> 35:06.440
Keep searching!

35:06.590 --> 35:07.320
Understood!

35:08.920 --> 35:09.480
Hold on.

35:12.920 --> 35:14.250
I've already searched.

35:14.360 --> 35:15.630
There's a cliff over there

35:15.630 --> 35:16.960
with bloodstains on it.

35:17.000 --> 35:18.730
Yan Xun took 2 arrows in the leg.

35:18.960 --> 35:22.030
He must have fallen off the cliff
and been crushed to pieces.

35:22.030 --> 35:22.560
Let's go.

35:30.960 --> 35:32.070
Take the body away.

35:51.440 --> 35:52.300
Your Highness,

35:52.510 --> 35:54.030
we've also been to the valley
on the other side.

35:54.030 --> 35:56.690
We did not find any trace
of the King of Great Yan.

36:06.480 --> 36:07.190
Let's go.

36:18.030 --> 36:18.690
Cheng Yuan.

36:21.880 --> 36:22.550
Cheng Yuan.

38:10.710 --> 38:11.630
Cheng Yuan...

38:16.670 --> 38:17.960
You can't die.

38:21.150 --> 38:22.030
Cheng Yuan...

38:25.320 --> 38:27.360
You can't die without my order!

38:29.760 --> 38:31.020
I want you to come back.

38:31.360 --> 38:32.030
Cheng Yuan.

38:35.320 --> 38:36.590
I want you to come back!

39:30.320 --> 39:32.670
Your Majesty, you, Great Yan, and I are

39:32.840 --> 39:33.840
one.

39:34.550 --> 39:37.710
Through life, death, honor,
and disgrace, to the very end,

39:37.710 --> 39:38.590
no matter when,

39:39.190 --> 39:41.960
I will always stand
by your side, Your Majesty.

39:44.040 --> 39:48.010
♪ The sky is so vast ♪

39:48.040 --> 39:50.520
♪ The dark clouds are gray ♪

39:52.910 --> 39:56.680
♪ The rain is falling ♪

39:56.700 --> 40:00.050
♪ The eagle is flying ♪

40:01.750 --> 40:05.530
♪ In the vast wilderness ♪

40:05.560 --> 40:09.030
♪ The wind blows ♪

40:11.050 --> 40:14.130
♪ I'm fearless of death ♪

40:14.360 --> 40:17.880
♪ And I'll never have regrets ♪

40:20.210 --> 40:27.730
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

40:27.480 --> 40:29.510
I don't want to see you again in my life.

40:29.210 --> 40:32.540
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

40:33.360 --> 40:34.480
I joined the army when I was young.

40:33.360 --> 40:36.550
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

40:35.150 --> 40:37.090
The military camp of Great Yan is my home.

40:37.090 --> 40:46.050
♪ In the vast world ♪

40:37.400 --> 40:40.600
The Black Eagle Army and you,
Your Majesty, are my family.

40:41.760 --> 40:42.960
Great Yan is so large,

40:43.880 --> 40:45.630
but I don't know where to go.

40:46.080 --> 40:49.480
♪ I have no origin ♪

40:47.230 --> 40:48.030
Cheng Yuan,

40:49.320 --> 40:50.630
I'll take you home.

40:50.140 --> 40:53.730
♪ And no destination ♪

40:54.300 --> 41:02.350
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

41:02.580 --> 41:10.850
♪ Is born to fly ♪

41:40.760 --> 41:41.550
Red Eagle,

41:43.070 --> 41:44.470
did Cheng Yuan send you?

41:57.550 --> 41:58.350
Your Majesty,

41:59.030 --> 42:01.290
Red Eagle knows the way back to Great Yan.

42:01.320 --> 42:02.520
It will take you home.

42:03.920 --> 42:05.580
Take good care of Helian Ling.

42:42.150 --> 42:43.630
Please wait, Your Highness!

42:43.630 --> 42:45.480
Chu Qiao is here to surrender.

42:46.150 --> 42:48.000
The third prophecy Jia Meng is to announce

42:48.000 --> 42:49.760
is that the Faceless God Sect will burn

42:49.760 --> 42:52.490
the current Chosen One to death
with sacred fire.

42:53.400 --> 42:54.200
Your Majesty,

42:55.840 --> 42:57.040
what did you just say?

42:58.030 --> 43:00.360
It is not appropriate for us
to meet again.

43:00.400 --> 43:01.460
Lord Zhuge, please

43:02.460 --> 43:03.310
behave yourself.
